702993f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ashford Street - Linden Boulevard
702993f-a.text:
Ashford Street, (foreground not sh wn), between Linden
Boulevard and Stanley Avenue (right). In the background on the
east side of Elton Street is seen the I. R. T. yards. Cleveland
Street extends north and south in the center of the view.
July 5, 1934
P. L. Sperr
